{
  "texts": [
    "The occupancy dataset was initially sourced to train classifiers for room occupancy detection [42].",
    "It contains more features for each instance, which could potentially serve as distractors when being processed for specific commands.",
    "Following the same standards, we formulated 20 distinct queries concerning its content: 5 at the basic level, 10 at the intermediate level, and 5 at the advanced level.",
    "And the prompts stayed the same for consistency, except for updates of task description.",
    "ResultsA generated script was considered valid if it a) ran successfully and b) addressed all the points in the query."
  ]
}